<div class="page-content">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

  <h2>Who We Are</h2>
  <p>Ragsdales's Heat &amp; Air LLC is a family-owned HVAC company serving California's Central Valley. Our website is <a href="https://www.ragsdalesheatandair.com">ragsdalesheatandair.com</a>. Questions about this policy can be directed to <a href="mailto:ragsdalesheatandair@outlook.com">ragsdalesheatandair@outlook.com</a> or by calling <a href="tel:2096336332">(209) 633-6332</a>.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>When you contact us, request a quote, or schedule service through our website, we collect information you voluntarily provide — such as your name, phone number, email address, and service address. This information is used solely to respond to your inquiry and schedule service.</p>

  <h2>Scheduling &amp; Service Software</h2>
  <p>We use HouseCall Pro to manage appointments and customer records. Information you provide when booking is stored within HouseCall Pro's platform. You can review their privacy policy at <a href="https://www.housecallpro.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">housecallpro.com/privacy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
  <p>We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website. Google Analytics collects anonymous data such as pages visited, time on site, and general geographic location. It does not identify you personally. You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by visiting <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</a>.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>Our website uses cookies to support basic site functions and Google Analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some site features may not work as expected.</p>

  <h2>We Do Not Sell Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

  <h2>California Residents</h2>
  <p>Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), California residents have the right to request what personal information we have collected and to ask us to delete it. To make a request, contact us at <a href="mailto:ragsdalesheatandair@outlook.com">ragsdalesheatandair@outlook.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>SMS / Text Messaging</h2>
  <p>If you have opted in to receive text messages from us, standard messaging rates may apply. Reply STOP at any time to unsubscribe. See our <a href="sms-terms.html">SMS Terms</a> for full details.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>Ragsdales's Heat &amp; Air LLC<br/>
  Escalon, CA<br/>
  <a href="tel:2096336332">(209) 633-6332</a><br/>
  <a href="mailto:ragsdalesheatandair@outlook.com">ragsdalesheatandair@outlook.com</a></p>
</div>

